Package pl.dfa.learner.automaton.pso

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PSOEventListener
    Event listener interface for integration with other software modules such as GUI
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryTransitionTable
    Binary transition table, initial version of the solution representation according to the documentation.
    DFARepresentation
    DFA representation for the PSO algorithm.
    DFARepresentationTest
    Tests the classes for representing solutions in the PSO
    DoubleTransitionTable
    Transition table for DFA-s with transitions encoded as double values.
    Evaluator
    Class used to evaluate solutions.
    MathUtil
    Several utility methods
    Particle
    Representation of a particle in the particle swarm optimisation metaheuristic.
    PSO
    Particle swarm optimisation (PSO) for learning the deterministic finite automata based on the learning set of inputs divided into accepted and unaccepted.
    PSOParams
    Parameters of the PSO metaheuristic
    PSOTest
    Runs the PSO for a given automaton
    PSOTestEven
    Runs the PSO for a given automaton
    PSOTestNonAccepting
    Runs the PSO for a given automaton
    Results
    Results of the PSO metaheuristic Keeps track of n best found solutions.
    SingletonRandom
    Singleton random number generator, to ensure all the objects share the same object (for randomisation quality enhancement):
    Solution
    Solution of the DFA learning problem suitable for use in PSO metaheuristic
    SolutionTest
    Test for the solution class
    Velocity
    Velocity of a PSO particle
    WordGeneratorTest
    Test of the word generator
    WordSet
    Set of a words, used to represent learning or testing set.
    WordSetGenerator
    Generates sets of words for training or testing the machine learning algorithm for learning the DFA functioning
